{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-post-js","path":"/Idea Pocket/Life Algorithm/life_pattern/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"춤추는망고의 기술 블로그","comment":{"utterances":"ensia96/ensia96.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"ensia96"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"eeeda440-b99f-5c64-8a6f-23c9bc75d414","tableOfContents":"","excerpt":"참고 사항 재택 기준(출퇴근 시간 제외) 보상 시간 = 업무, 공부에 신경 쓰지 않는 시간 1시간 기준, 50분은 집중, 10분은 휴식 참고 영상(집중, 휴식 비율) https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=inhsROAhhPY https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4YoxyuuCwt0 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3WxdLVip66o 20210724 - 전 직장에서의 생활 패턴을 기준으로 코드 기반 구성","html":"<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> datetime <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> time\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">LifePattern</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token triple-quoted-string string\">'''\n    생활 패턴을 규격화하는 클래스\n    '''</span>\n    OPTIMAL_SLEEP_TIME <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">8</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 최적의 수면 시간</span>\n    MINIMAL_SLLEP_TIME <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 최소한의 수면 시간</span>\n    MEAL_AND_REST_TIME <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 식사 및 휴식 시간</span>\n    BASE_TIME <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">'shower'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 샤워 시간</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">'concentration'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 집중 시간</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">'rest'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 휴식 시간</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">'reward'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 보상 시간</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">__init__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">**</span>kwargs<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        default <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">'wake_up'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 기상 시간</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">'routine_start'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 일상 시작</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">'routine_end'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">18</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 일상 종료</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">'lunch'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">12</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 점심 시간</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">'dinner'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 저녁 시간</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> key <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> default<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            <span class=\"token builtin\">setattr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> key<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> time<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>kwargs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>get<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>key<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> default<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>key<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n</code></pre></div>\n<details><summary>메모</summary>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">기상(~ 09:00)\n+ 샤워(1시간/09:00 ~ 10:00)\n+ 오전(2시간/10:00 ~ 12:00)\n+ 점심(1시간/12:00 ~ 13:00)\n+ 오후(5시간/13:00 ~ 18:00)\n+ TIL(1시간/18:00 ~ 19:00)\n+ 샤워(1시간/19:00 ~ 20:00)\n+ 저녁(1시간/20:00 ~ 21:00)\n+ 보상(4시간/21:00 ~ 01:00)\n+ 수면(8시간/01:00 ~ 09:00)\n\n업무 시간(회사) : '10:00 ~ 12:00', '13:00 ~ 18:00'</code></pre></div>\n<p>참고 사항</p>\n<ul>\n<li>재택 기준(출퇴근 시간 제외)</li>\n<li>보상 시간 = 업무, 공부에 신경 쓰지 않는 시간</li>\n<li>1시간 기준, 50분은 집중, 10분은 휴식</li>\n</ul>\n<p>참고 영상(집중, 휴식 비율)</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=inhsROAhhPY\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=inhsROAhhPY</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4YoxyuuCwt0\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4YoxyuuCwt0</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3WxdLVip66o\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3WxdLVip66o</a></li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<details><summary>변경 기록</summary>\n<ul>\n<li>20210724 - 전 직장에서의 생활 패턴을 기준으로 코드 기반 구성</li>\n</ul>\n</details>","frontmatter":{"title":"life_pattern","tags":["Algorithm","Pseudocode"],"date":"July 24, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Idea Pocket/Life Algorithm/life_pattern/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Experience Storage/TIL/2021/07/22~28/20210723-til/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"20210723-TIL","category":"TIL","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Experience Storage/TIL/2021/07/22~28/20210724-til/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"20210724-TIL","category":"TIL","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","4018478212"]}